{"tid":1839383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港沙士互助會: 如果情況持續惡化，政府必須考慮禁止所有內地訪客來港，直至內地病情有改善的趨勢。","createTime":"2020-01-24T11:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T13:24:28.000Z","uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0abbe12c83be4b878aedf2b3439554b7844b6ef7","tid":1839383,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504652-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504652-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77RPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=a0f52bce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504652-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c94979ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504652-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港沙士互助會表示，強烈關注近日新型肺炎疫情，希望政府能汲取2003年沙士的教訓，做好防疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n互助會要求政府採取一切可行的措施，減低本港市民受新型肺炎的影響，包括禁止過去一個月曾到訪武漢的非本地人士進入香港，所有由內地到港的訪客或香港居民必須填寫健康申報表。如果情況持續惡化，政府必須考慮禁止所有內地訪客來港，直至內地病情有改善的趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n互助會呼籲市民注意個人衛生及提高個人防疫意識，若出現發燒及呼吸道感染徵狀，應馬上就診，又建議市民盡可能隨身攜帶消毒噴霧、消毒濕纸巾等，在人多擠逼的地方，務必戴上口罩。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由呢個協會講特別有聲"},{"pid":"ebf877754b89e9431d07a69624a6b7014655e1d1","tid":1839383,"uid":127735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"香港政府：歡迎內地同胞來港看症"},{"pid":"ecb40d999932bde937c0c95f3f14542bc7ce56b5","tid":1839383,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e501e5b74f8343317bfb07bd235b75739721eda3","tid":1839383,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ccc826de8e3dfe56d792dc7c6ad8563407a559","tid":1839383,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"林鄭條柒碌03年做緊社會褔利署署長，無可能唔知SARS家屬慘況"},{"pid":"bad29c47b68557ac8abef7a4595c054166a4f881","tid":1839383,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d4c9e73753298c7657a541d9065a19bf396b0ac","tid":1839383,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"狗官死全家 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"0ffd7c55e6e447c6398e04d7f749153e0370782b","tid":1839383,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"林鄭，你記唔記得SARS呀"},{"pid":"5c7d9604ab62115f9e084c31d2074b601b42695b","tid":1839383,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}